{"tid":1837152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[鍵盤戰線]係時候反滲透武漢人啦","createTime":"2020-01-23T13:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T11:33:23.000Z","uid":229020,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"84d961cccee61d012819150f5ea27603959143b3","tid":1837152,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"武漢同支國各地而家為咗抗疫，謠言滿天飛<br />\n中共網絡監控應該疲於奔命<br />\n各位有冇諗過趁亂煽動革命思想畀武漢百姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，武漢而家封城，佢哋應該活喺恐慌當中（或將會）<br />\n我哋可以灌輸中共會點樣放棄、由佢哋自身自滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，班大陸人開始唔信中共媒體，<br />\n佢哋會翻牆到twitter同tg睇消息，<br />\n我哋可把握網絡主場優勢帶風向，<br />\n例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2JFyHF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2JFyHF.png&h=f7fdba3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TviBRum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTviBRum.png&h=7b71c82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫時得呢條link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wuhanquarantinefrom20200123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwuhanquarantinefrom20200123&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=fda7534a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wuhanquarantinefrom20200123</a><br />\nchannel入面個公海有一啲武漢人<br />\n各位twiter手足係時候做嘢啦<br />\n<br />\n星星之火，可以燎原<br />\n光復香港，指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73c6692b90c04b5e4bd7721bd6e682d1d3246c9","tid":1837152,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e382577aa956caa61f98841c54c9ebc05a50e718","tid":1837152,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"